results.name: Numerators of resistance values that can be obtained from a network of exactly 10 one-ohm resistors, but not from any network with fewer than 10 one-ohm resistors. Denominators are in A338590.
comment: The A338197(k)/2 initial terms of this sequence are also the numerators of the corresponding sorted lists of resistance values that can be achieved by exactly k resistors for all k < 10.
link: Hugo Pfoertner, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..2639
xref: The initial terms of this sequence are also the numerators to be used together with the denominators given in A338595, A338596, A338597, A338598, A338599.
results.author: _Hugo Pfoertner_, Nov 06 2020
